text:
⚜️Designed in a circular shape, the Colonial Garden showcase some of  the cash crops cultivated during the Colonial era in Singapore.
⚜️These plantation crops includes the much sort after spices, coffee, gambier, nutmeg and rubber which brought about trades between the East and West.
⚜️A tranquil and shady Garden located just a few minutes walk from the Meadow and Supertrees Grove.
